@startuml
!include ../../_common/style.puml

title distributed-lock-component 模块结构图

package "distributed-lock-component" as root {
  package "distributed-lock-api" as api
  package "distributed-lock-core" as core

  package "distributed-lock-provider" as provider {
    package "distributed-lock-provider-redis" as redis
  }

  package "distributed-lock-starter" as starter
  package "distributed-lock-demo" as demo
}

core ..> api : depends on API
redis ..> api : use API/SPI model
redis ..> core : use core SPI/model
starter ..> api : expose beans
starter ..> core : auto-config core
starter ..> redis : auto-config Redis provider
demo ..> starter : use starter

note right of api
  API 层：
  业务可见接口与结果模型。
end note

note right of core
  Core 层：
  通用流程编排、waiter、watchdog、
  事件、指标和结果收敛。
end note

note right of redis
  Redis Provider：
  一期默认底层实现。
end note

@enduml
